    • Method Detail

      • setConfiguration

        public void setConfiguration(AppboyConfig config)
        Sets an AppboyConfig into the override cache. The cache is not cleared beforehand, merging the new configuration with the old. Old key values get clobbered by new key values.
        Parameters:
        config - the new configuration to set into the cache.
